---
title: Hearty Chicken & Potato Coconut Curry with Brown Rice & Cashews
description: With its gentle warming heat and colourful veggies, a rich and creamy Indian chicken curry is a favourite meal for good
reason! Whip up this version with turnip, carrot and potato, plus wholesome brown rice that'll leave you
embracing a modern classic.
